          best data science training institute in Bangalore.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary inline-block">Enquire Now</a>
          <a href="/courses" class="btn-primary inline-block">Our Courses</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-14">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 hover:border-yellow-400 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-yellow-400/10 text-center overflow-hidden">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Trainer</p>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-black">11+ Years Industry Experience</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 hover:border-yellow-400 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-yellow-400/10 text-center overflow-hidden">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Course Duration</p>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-black">8 months | 320+ Hrs</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 hover:border-yellow-400 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-yellow-400/10 text-center overflow-hidden">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Certificate</p>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-black">Course Completion & Internship</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 hover:border-yellow-400 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-yellow-400/10 text-center overflow-hidden">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Internships & Placement</p>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-black">100% Placement Assistance</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 self-center md:mt-6 relative">
