                src="/images/data_science_courses_in_bangalore.png"
                alt="Data science courses in Bangalore"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                width="960"
                height="720"
                decoding="async"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2 self-center">
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-400 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Hands-on Data Science Training in Bangalore</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Are you looking for the most comprehensive Data Science course in Bangalore,
            Rajajinagar? While Harvard called it the &quot;sexiest job&quot; back in 2012, in 2026, Data
            Science has evolved into the backbone of the global economy. At Corpnce, we provide a
            future-proof curriculum that doesn&apos;t just teach data—it teaches you how to lead in the
            age of Generative AI and MLOps.
            </p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mt-6 mb-3">
            Why 2026 is the Year to Start Your Data Science Journey
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The landscape of data has shifted. To be job-ready in Bangalore&apos;s elite tech parks
            today, you need more than just basic statistics.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <span class="font-bold">Massive Job Growth:</span> India alone is projected to have over
              1.1 million active data science roles by the end of 2026.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-bold">High Salary Potential:</span> The average salary for Data
              Scientists in Bangalore now ranges from ₹7.5L to ₹15L for early-career professionals,
              with AI specialists touching ₹25L+.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-bold">Industry Adoption:</span> Over 72% of companies have now
              integrated AI into at least one business function, creating a desperate need for
              skilled architects.
            </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <style>
        .image-scan::before {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          inset: -40% -60%;
          background: linear-gradient(
            120deg,
            transparent 45%,
            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35) 50%,
            transparent 55%
          );
          transform: translateX(-60%);
          animation: scanSweep 6.5s ease-in-out infinite;
          pointer-events: none;
        }
        .image-scan::after {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          inset: 0;
          background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18) 1px, transparent 1px);
          background-size: 18px 18px;
          opacity: 0.18;
          mix-blend-mode: screen;
          pointer-events: none;
        }
        @keyframes scanSweep {
          0% {
            transform: translateX(-60%);
          }
          50% {
            transform: translateX(10%);
          }
          100% {
            transform: translateX(60%);
          }
        }
      </style>

      <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-10 shadow-sm">
        <span class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-16 -right-16 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-yellow-400/10 blur-3xl"></span>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-4">
              What is Data Science and Why is it Essential Today?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Data Science is the multidisciplinary field that blends domain expertise, advanced
              programming, and mathematical rigor to turn raw noise into actionable intelligence.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              In 2026, the era of "gut-feeling" leadership is over. Modern organizations rely on Data
              Science to navigate a complex global market. By integrating traditional analytics with
              cutting-edge Generative AI, Machine Learning, and Deep Learning, businesses can now
              predict market shifts, automate complex tasks, and reduce operational risk to near
              zero.
            </p>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-4">
              The Massive Talent Gap: Why You Should Care
            </h2>
