                The demand for Data Science and AI professionals in India has reached a critical
                tipping point. While previous years saw a steady rise, the current "AI Revolution"
                has created an unprecedented shortage of skilled talent.
              </p>
              <p>
                <span class="font-bold">GROWING DEFICIT:</span> Recent industry reports indicate that
                while demand for AI and Data roles has surpassed 1.5 million professionals, the
                supply gap remains at nearly 30%, leaving lakhs of high-paying positions vacant.
              </p>
              <p>
                <span class="font-bold">EXPLOSIVE GROWTH:</span> Demand for Data Science architects
                and AI engineers has seen a multi-fold increase compared to traditional software
                roles, particularly in tech hubs like Bangalore.
              </p>
              <p>
                <span class="font-bold">THE "GENAI" FACTOR:</span> Since the surge of LLMs, companies
                are no longer just looking for "analysts"—they are looking for Full-Stack Data
                Scientists who can deploy intelligent models in real-time.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-yellow-400/20 blur-3xl"></div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-yellow-200 bg-yellow-50/60 p-4">
              <img
                src="/images/data_science_2026.png"
                alt="Data science 2026 visualization"
                class="h-72 w-full rounded-xl object-cover md:h-96"
                width="720"
                height="480"
                decoding="async"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Business Impact</p>
                <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-black">Predictive insights in real time</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Automation</p>
                <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-black">Smarter workflows at scale</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
