            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black mb-4">Salary Trends in Bangalore</h4>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">
                  <span>Freshers (0–1 year)</span>
                  <span>₹6L – ₹8L per annum</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-200">
                  <div class="h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 w-[32%]"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">
                  <span>Freshers without AI skills</span>
                  <span>₹3L per annum</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-200">
                  <div class="h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400 w-[18%]"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">
                  <span>Mid-level (4–8 years)</span>
                  <span>₹12L – ₹25L per annum</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-200">
                  <div class="h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 w-full"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-4">
              Specialized Roles (GenAI/MLOps): demand for Generative AI and LLM skills grew by 60% last
              year, with specialists commanding premiums of 30–50% over traditional analysts.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="mt-4 md:mt-2">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mt-4 mb-4">Learned Skills from Data Science Courses</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li><span class="font-bold">Core Programming:</span> Python (the industry standard) and essential libraries like Pandas, NumPy, and Scikit-learn.</li>
            <li><span class="font-bold">The AI Suite:</span> Generative AI (LLMs), Deep Learning, and Neural Networks.</li>
            <li><span class="font-bold">Predictive Analytics:</span> Advanced Machine Learning algorithms for forecasting and classification.</li>
            <li><span class="font-bold">Data Engineering:</span> Data Wrangling, Exploration, and ETL (Extract, Transform, Load) processes.</li>
            <li><span class="font-bold">Visualization & Storytelling:</span> Creating impactful narratives using tools like PowerBI, Tableau, and Seaborn.</li>
            <li><span class="font-bold">Production Readiness:</span> Deploying models on the Cloud and mastering MLOps basics.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Download the Course Curriculum</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
