            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2" for="curriculum-phone">Phone</label>
              <input
                id="curriculum-phone"
                name="phone"
                type="tel"
                required
                class="w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-gray-900 focus:border-yellow-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400/40"
                placeholder="+91 98765 43210"
              />
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn-primary w-full">Download Curriculum</button>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
              By submitting, you agree to receive course information from Corpnce.
            </p>
          </form>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 via-white to-white border border-yellow-100 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-900 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mb-4">
          Designed For
        </span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Who Should Do The Data Science Course?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          The beauty of Data Science in 2026 is its universality. We have designed this program for anyone with a logical mindset and a hunger for problem-solving.
        </p>
