            <strong class="text-black">Corporate Leaders & Managers:</strong> Leverage "Decision Intelligence" to lead teams with data-backed strategies.
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <strong class="text-black">Career Switchers:</strong> Professionals from Finance, Healthcare, or Retail looking to pivot into high-growth tech roles.
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <strong class="text-black">Technical Minds:</strong> Software developers, Database admins, and BI professionals wanting to upgrade to AI-driven architectures.
