              <div class="h-1 w-12 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-2">
              EXECUTIVE DATA SCIENCE & AI STRATEGY
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-4">
              The Leadership Blueprint for the 2026 Data Economy
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
              This high-impact program is meticulously designed for Top Executives, Senior Managers, and Business Leaders who need to move beyond the hype and lead with "Decision Intelligence." In 2026, leadership isn't just about managing people; it's about managing AI-human hybrid workflows. No prior programming knowledge is required.
